fields.placeholder: COPPA - CHILDREN'S ONLINE PRIVACY PROTECTION ACT
fields.name: COPPA - CHILDREN'S ONLINE PRIVACY PROTECTION ACT
fields.value: AS PER COPPA REQUIREMENTS, THIS IS TO CERTIFY THAT THE ABOVE NAMED PLAYER IS MY DEPENDENT AND HAS MY PERMISSION TO USE AND PARTICIPATE ON THE RUSH SOCCER WEBSITE. I UNDERSTAND THAT RUSH SOCCER COLLECTS CERTAIN PIECES OF INFORMATION FROM CHILDREN AND THAT THESE ITEMS ARE USED FOR THE SOLE PURPOSE OF WEB PROGRAMS AND EMAIL COMMUNICATIONS RELATED TO THE RUSH. THIS INFORMATION WILL NEVER BE SOLD TO THIRD PARTIES. THE INFORMATION COLLECTED IS TO HELP CONFIRM RUSH MEMBERSHIP, AS WELL AS POPULATE CERTAIN PROGRAMS AND WEB PAGES WITH USER INFORMATION. I UNDERSTAND THAT RUSH SOCCER POPULATES THESE AREAS WITH ONLY ABSOLUTELY NECESSARY INFORMATION.

fields.name: Injury Liability
fields.value: I understand that participation in sports requires an acceptance of the risk of an injury. I understand that I/my child may be permanently injured while playing sports and accept the risk. I understand I/my child must follow all the rules of my sport. I understand that I/my child must refrain from practice or play while injured or ill, whether or not I am/my child is receiving medical treatment and during medical treatment until I am/my child is discharged from treatment or given permission by a physician to return to participation despite continuing treatment.

fields.name: Image Rights
fields.value: From time to time, Rush Soccer may post photos and images related to my son/daughter on websites and social media accounts related to soccer during and, or after his/her participation with Rush Soccer.

fields.name: Consent of Treatment
fields.value: I understand that I/my child may be injured while participating in athletics with Rush Soccer. I authorize the coach, team parent, or athletic trainer to seek any emergency medical care that may become necessary while participating or traveling with Rush Soccer. I assume the financial responsibility for any medical treatment for me/my child. I also authorize the athletic trainer to administer treatments related to injury prevention and rehabilitation.
